{
  "texts": [
    "Users can drag the slider any time to the right to increase the weight on an attribute toward a positive \"admit\" decision or to the left to reduce its contribution.",
    "Alternatively, users can directly input contribution values in a box below the slider.",
    "Slide bars in Figure 5-2 and Figure 5-4 are interconnected, so as those in Figure 5-3 and Figure 5-6.",
    "Values within the \"overall prediction bar\" reflect the cumulative values from the \"concrete opinion bars. \"",
    "Any changes in the dimension-level bars immediately update the overall prediction."
  ]
}